        <updateDate>2017-07-05T19:15:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Sustainable Water Infrastructure Investment Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to exempt tax-exempt facility bonds for sewage and water supply facilities from the state volume caps on private activity bonds. </p>]]></text>
